---

This model wrapper integrates ProGen2, an autoregressive protein language model
by Erik Nijkamp, Jeffrey A. Ruffolo, Eli N. Weinstein, Nikhil Naik, and Ali
Madani (Salesforce Research).

Source: https://github.com/salesforce/progen
Model weights: released by Salesforce under BSD-3-Clause
Paper: "ProGen2: Exploring the Boundaries of Protein Language Models"
(Cell Systems, 2023; arXiv:2206.13517)

The ProGen2 code and weights are released by Salesforce under the BSD-3-Clause
license above (see https://github.com/salesforce/progen/blob/main/LICENSE). The
underlying model architecture is based on GPT-J (Apache-2.0).
